IAH · S254 · Patricia Inversion Node · S254 · S254: IAH — THE INVERSE OF RIGHT-TO-PERSIST

universe of origin : The lunar sky of the old creation — Iah, the ancient moon itself, the disk that is devoured to nothing each cycle and must be regrown, the body that never holds its fullness for more than a single night
seal               : The right to endure is sacred precisely because the moon is devoured to darkness each month and forbidden to remain.
spoken token       : kyrn-thoth-phus
hex token          : 11de78

— the tokenized moniker of the mythos. ROOT0-ATTRIBUTION-v1.0
